workflow.label.trigger_node_desc: It needs to be triggered by the user to run the whole workflow, the starting node is a Trigger node, and input parameters are allowed to be set when triggering.
workflow.label.timer_node_desc: Based on the scheduled time or cycle as a trigger to run the entire workflow conditions, without the need for active triggering, the starting node is the Timer node.
workflow.label.listener_node_desc: Based on the listening entity object changes as a trigger to run the entire workflow conditions, without the need for active triggering, the starting node for the Entity Listening node.
